* SEP-41 Fungible Token\non Stellar with\nOpenZeppelin

** The standard
*** 10 required functions
*** i128 amounts
*** approve carries\nlive_until_ledger
*** burn is mandatory
*** total_supply and mint\nare NOT in SEP-41

** Deployment paths
*** Classic asset + SAC
**** No Rust, no Wasm
**** Native DEX, anchors,\npath payments
**** Trustlines, 7 decimals
*** Custom Soroban token
**** stellar-tokens crate
**** Full control of logic
**** No native DEX listing
*** Classic asset\n+ OZ SAC admin
**** Wrapper: explicit\nadmin entry points
**** Generic: __check_auth

** Library architecture
*** FungibleToken trait\n(contracttrait)
*** type ContractType
**** Base
**** AllowList
**** BlockList
**** RWA
*** ContractOverrides\nroutes each method
*** Extensions are mutually\nexclusive at compile time
*** High-level fns vs\n_no_auth low-level fns

** Extensions
*** Burnable\n(needed for SEP-41)
*** Capped\n(check_cap before mint)
*** Ownable\n(only_owner macro)
*** Pausable\n(when_not_paused macro)
*** Votes, Vault

** Build and deploy
*** stellar contract build
**** cargo build fails:\nspec_shaking_v2
*** stellar keys generate --fund
*** stellar contract deploy\n-- <constructor args>
*** stellar contract invoke

** Storage and TTL
*** instance:\nMeta, TotalSupply, Cap
*** persistent:\nBalance(Address)
*** temporary:\nAllowance(owner, spender)
*** Reads extend TTL,\nwrites do not
